basic.c:6:3: use_g_settings_typed: Use g_settings_set_string (settings, "name", "hello") instead of g_settings_set_value with g_variant_new for type safety
basic.c:7:3: use_g_settings_typed: Use g_settings_set_int (settings, "count", 42) instead of g_settings_set_value with g_variant_new for type safety
basic.c:9:13: use_g_settings_typed: Use g_settings_get_int (settings, "count") instead of g_variant_get_* with g_settings_get_value for type safety
